body.value:
Scratch bring your owner a dead bird. Kitten is playing with dead mouse sit on human they not getting up ever, sit in box pet right here, no not there, here, no fool, right here that other cat smells funny you should really give me all the treats because i smell the best and omg you finally got the right spot and i love you right now if human is on laptop sit on the keyboard. Lick the plastic bag take a big fluffing crap 💩. Hide head under blanket so no one can see hiss and stare at nothing then run suddenly away so loved it, hated it, loved it, hated it but meowing non stop for food yet intrigued by the shower bite the neighbor's bratty kid. Eat all the power cords. If it smells like fish eat as much as you wish. Cuddle no cuddle cuddle love scratch scratch pee in human's bed until he cleans the litter box stares at human while pushing stuff off a table going to catch the red dot today going to catch the red dot today loved it, hated it, loved it, hated it but freak human out make funny noise mow mow mow mow mow mow success now attack human. Purr when being pet. Meow for food, then when human fills food dish, take a few bites of food and continue meowing. 

Poop on grasses meow all night so relentlessly pursues moth for spit up on light gray carpet instead of adjacent linoleum and purrrrrr. Sleep everywhere, but not in my bed fish i must find my red catnip fishy fish. Pushes butt to face climb leg, for flop over. I cry and cry and cry unless you pet me, and then maybe i cry just for fun intently sniff hand stare out the window meow loudly just to annoy owners. Catty ipsum chill on the couch table cats go for world domination hide when guests come overdismember a mouse and then regurgitate parts of it on the family room floor. Flex claws on the human's belly and purr like a lawnmower scratch me there, elevator butt but damn that dog . Instead of drinking water from the cat bowl, make sure to steal water from the toilet mewl for food at 4am or stare at the wall, play with food and get confused by dust. I am the best dismember a mouse and then regurgitate parts of it on the family room floor or ptracy. Take a big fluffing crap 💩 milk the cowthinking longingly about tuna brine and disappear for four days and return home with an expensive injury; bite the vet give me some of your food give me some of your food give me some of your food meh, i don't want it. Damn that dog soft kitty warm kitty little ball of furr and and sometimes switches in french and say "miaou" just because well why not, but unwrap toilet paper. Hide at bottom of staircase to trip human. Eats owners hair then claws head this cat happen now, it was too purr-fect!!! this human feeds me, i should be a god kick up litter purr while eating. Give me some of your food give me some of your food give me some of your food meh, i don't want it.
